      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 5.3156162873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、大体書けたわね。後はこれを……\nあら、千紗",
      "startTime": 6.3312866957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "それって、雑誌のお誕生日企画のアンケートだよね\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』、だっけ",
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、誕生日に合わせて\nやってみたかったことを叶えてくれるみたいなの",
      "startTime": 20.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど今、書き終わったところよ",
      "startTime": 23.4768482048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わ～、見てもいい？\nふむふむ、お姉ちゃんのやってみたいことは……",
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "『最近疲れ気味な千紗のために\nマッサージを勉強したい』……",
      "startTime": 37.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "『月ストのために、ランキング上位のアイドルを\n研究して今後に生かしたい』……",
      "startTime": 45.2000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃん、私のためとか、月ストのためとか\nこれじゃあいつもと変わんないよ～",
      "startTime": 55.5000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}